! Morphological Transducer for Japanese

Multichar_Symbols

! Part of speech categories
%<n%>   ! Noun
%<pn%>  ! Proper noun
%<v%>	! Verb
%<adj%> ! Adjective
%<adv%> ! Adverb
%<cnjcoo%> ! Coordinating conjunction
%<ij%>  ! Interjection
%<prn%> ! Pronoun
%<cop%>	! Copula
%<num%> ! Numeral
%<det%> ! Determiner

%<dem%> ! Demonstrative

%<top%> ! toponym (should probably be changed?)

%<attr%> ! for na adjectives

! Particles
%<tpc%> ! Topic
%<nom%>  ! Nominative
%<gen%>  ! Genitive
%<acc%>  ! Accusative
%<dat%>  ! Dative
%<quot%> ! Quotative
%<all%> ! Allative
%<abl%>  ! Ablative
%<ins%>  ! Instrumental
%<com%>  ! Comitative
%<term%> ! Terminative
%<mod%>  ! For final particles
%<abs%>  ! For things that don't have postpositions

! -alisers
%<nz%>  ! Nominaliser
%<az%>  ! Adverbaliser
%<vz%>  ! Verbaliser

! Pronoun-related
%<p1%>   ! First person
%<p2%>   ! Second person
%<p3%>   ! Third person
%<pers%> ! Personal

! verb suffixes
%<vol%>  ! Volitional
%<neg%>  ! Negative
%<past%> ! Past
%<imp%>  ! Imperative
%<npst%> ! Non-past
!conditional?
%<caus%>  ! Causative
%<pot%>   ! Potential
%<pass%>  ! Passive
%<cvb_te%> ! te form, because I don't know what it is
%<prog%> ! progressive

! Number morphology
%<pl%>  ! Plural
%<sg%>  ! Singular

! Formality
%<pol%>	! Polite
%<ifml%>! Informal

!Punctuation
%<sent%>
%<cm%>
%<lquot%>
%<rquot%>
%<lpar%>
%<rpar%>

! Other symbols
%>      ! Morpheme boundary
%{っ%} ! for use in ta and te form
%{a%} ! for use in neg form
%{た%} ! for use in ta form
%{て%} ! for te form
%{i%} ! for adverbial form

